        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Liogenys ophtalmica Frey, 1973 male holotype views: A) dorsal, C) labels, E) head dorsal, H) head ventral; male paratype views: B) dorsal, D) labels, F) head dorsal, G) head lateral, I) head ventral, J) detail of antenna with accessorial appendix, K) lateral, and parameres views: L) dorsal, M) lateral. Abbreviations:AAP: accessorial appendix of antenna, ANT: funicle and club of antenna, CLP: clypeus, EY: eye, LBR: labrum, SCP: scape of antenna, PLP: maxillary palp." ;
